revision.text: ==Sprinklotad Leveling Strategy== The most efficient way to gain experience for the [[Sprinklotad]] is to equip the fully-leveled [[Sprayduck]] and surround 4 Kasibs with Cheris in the following way. Keep replanting Cheris as they wither while either shoveling or harvesting extra Kasibs that sprout.
